    <item>
      <title>埃塞俄比亚考虑发行巨额债券以解决国有企业债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/ethiopia-eyes-big-bond-offer-to-settle-debt-of-state-owned-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃塞俄比亚计划发行 9000 亿比尔（74 亿美元）的债券，以偿还几家国有企业的债务，这些债务已拖累了这个东非国家最大的贷方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/ethiopia-eyes-big-bond-offer-to-settle-debt-of-state-owned-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 13:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
